summary: Phoebe: You are an anomaly in so many ways, because you’re 26 and yet you’re 2,000 at the same time; you have this wisdom and...
caption:
Phoebe: You are an anomaly in so many ways, because you’re 26 and yet you’re 2,000 at the same time; you have this wisdom and self-assurance that only trees have.

Jodie: [laughing] Ah, I’m a tree!

Phoebe: But you also express this powerful beauty. Every single person who works with you wants to talk about how wonderful you are to work with, and how the set comes alive with joy and lightness when you’re there. That’s also something that comes from inside of you, there’s a goodness and a fierce work ethic, without any ego. I want to know when it was you realised you were so fantastic?

Jodie: Shut up! [Phoebe makes an evil laughing sound in the background].

summary: I left tumblr for a couple of days and DRAAAAMAAAA ... The interviews thing,...come on guys, even tough i have my opinions about...
body:
I left tumblr for a couple of days and DRAAAAMAAAA … The interviews thing,…come on guys, even tough i have my opinions about the finale, this series is clearly NOT QUEERBAITING! This series is a character study, these two need to evolve, accept a lot of thing about themselves, then their romantic/sexual culmination thing will be truly meaningful.

It is valid to have unpopular opinions and all that but be open to others opinions and discuss, i mean it’s fun and estimulating to hear constructive criticism AND also enjoy the fucking show and respect the people working on it.

Anyways, kudos to BBC beacuse the UK Campaign IS AWESOME

summary: i know it’s fun to make theories about ke and ship whoever you may ship, but at the end of the day, people need to remember that...
body:
i know it’s fun to make theories about ke and ship whoever you may ship, but at the end of the day, people need to remember that it’s legit a fictional work… it’s not real, people!! so people may interpret the fiction however they want and you have no way of telling me or anyone else how to see the characters or their emotions/mentalities.

sorry to be brash, but someone tried to explain to me something I already fully realize about the show. please don’t try to come at me like I’m some little idiot; I’m free to interpret eve & villanelle’s relationship/interactions however I want sweetie 🤷‍♀️
